rComments: Prof is a nice person, but try to avoid her ENG1120 class if possible. Content is too vague and hard to get a good grade. Lectures drag on and class is hard to endure. sorry :/

The lectures were brutally boring. The concept of place she bases the class around is very narrow for a first year course. If being taught about indigeneity by a European settler bothers you, skip this class.
Prof Lewis is a great teacher, she is very understanding and cares for her students. Lectures can sometimes be quite boring but overall great person!
